{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it a specific criminal offence not to notify the authorities of a death",
        "additional_details": "Clear laws must require anyone aware of a death to notify authorities immediately, with serious consequences for neglect or deception, to protect the vulnerable and ensure dignity in death.",
        "background": "I would like it to become a specific criminal offence to not report a dead body or a death if you are in the company of said individual when they pass or if you are aware of one.",
